#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:114
msgid ""
"To install the KDE Plasma meta package with KDE Frameworks, Plasma Desktop "
"and Applications execute:"
msgstr ""
"Для установки мета-пакета KDE Plasma, включающего KDE Frameworks, Plasma "
"Desktop и Applications, выполните:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install kde\n"
msgstr "# pkg install kde\n"

#. type: Title ====
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Minimal KDE Plasma installation"
msgstr "Минимальная установка KDE Plasma"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:124
msgid "To install a minimal KDE Plasma execute:"
msgstr "Для установки минимальной версии KDE Plasma выполните:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install plasma6-plasma\n"
msgstr "# pkg install plasma6-plasma\n"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:134
msgid ""
"This installation is *really* minimal.  Konsole must be installed separately "
"executing:"
msgstr ""
"Эта установка *действительно* минимальна. Konsole необходимо установить "
"отдельно, выполнив:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
